{"tid":658431,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇Razor Blade Stealth / Dell XPS 9370","createTime":"2018-05-09T03:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T04:30:32.000Z","uid":148636,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"58f758114bd12b53c7d30cff7e5d376c55ea3e6f","tid":658431,"uid":148636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"細佬我係電腦白痴一個, 想請教下巴打們<br />\n本身用緊Macbook Air<br />\n一般黎講都係睇下youtube, 上下網咁<br />\n最近轉左份新工經常要帶電腦出trip做野<br />\n女朋友又想要部laptop做下普通文書野<br />\n所以打算自己換部ultrabook, macbook air俾女朋友用<br />\n<br />\n而家睇中左Razor Blade Stealth <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Razer-Touchscreen-Ultrabook-Generation-i7-8550U/dp/B077C2VN4D/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1525836448&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=razer+blade+stealth\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRazer-Touchscreen-Ultrabook-Generation-i7-8550U%2Fdp%2FB077C2VN4D%2Fref%3Dsr_1_3%3Fie%3DUTF8%26qid%3D1525836448%26sr%3D8-3%26keywords%3Drazer%2Bblade%2Bstealth&d=TSnP4WbJqntNZ1aUBGXHqi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c3e0eacb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Razer-Touchscreen-Ultrabook-Generation-i7-8550U/dp/B077C2VN4D/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1525836448&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=razer+blade+stealth</a><br />\n同 Dell XPS 9370<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Dell-InfinityEdge-Display-i7-8550U-Fingerprint/dp/B079MJ27SW/ref=pd_sbs_147_2?_encoding=UTF8&amp;pd_rd_i=B079MJ27SW&amp;pd_rd_r=5BJWTWT0VFV1BVF0RR62&amp;pd_rd_w=3ffk1&amp;pd_rd_wg=4DMli&amp;psc=1&amp;refRID=5BJWTWT0VFV1BVF0RR62&amp;dpID=41FzSBuP3JL&amp;preST=_SX300_QL70_&amp;dpSrc=detail\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDell-InfinityEdge-Display-i7-8550U-Fingerprint%2Fdp%2FB079MJ27SW%2Fref%3Dpd_sbs_147_2%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26pd_rd_i%3DB079MJ27SW%26pd_rd_r%3D5BJWTWT0VFV1BVF0RR62%26pd_rd_w%3D3ffk1%26pd_rd_wg%3D4DMli%26psc%3D1%26refRID%3D5BJWTWT0VFV1BVF0RR62%26dpID%3D41FzSBuP3JL%26preST%3D_SX300_QL70_%26dpSrc%3Ddetail&d=TSnP4WbJqntNZ1aUBGXHqi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e20262bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Dell-InfinityEdge-Display-i7-8550U-Fingerprint/dp/B079MJ27SW/ref=pd_sbs_147_2?_encoding=UTF8&amp;pd_rd_i=B079MJ27SW&amp;pd_rd_r=5BJWTWT0VFV1BVF0RR62&amp;pd_rd_w=3ffk1&amp;pd_rd_wg=4DMli&amp;psc=1&amp;refRID=5BJWTWT0VFV1BVF0RR62&amp;dpID=41FzSBuP3JL&amp;preST=_SX300_QL70_&amp;dpSrc=detail</a><br />\n<br />\n主要用途都係做文書, office野, 上網, 睇片<br />\n因為有console所以對打機無特別大要求, 可能會玩FM同LOL, 唔追求畫質, low setting ~ 40 - 50 FPS 已經ok, 大作呀食雞呀個d都唔會玩<br />\n<br />\n最主要個concern都係要帶住周圍走, office, 出trip, 屋企都係用佢<br />\n如果呢兩部2選1巴打們會建議邊部? 或者有其他choice?<br />\n<br />\n另外有個問題就係, 而家好似興d ultrabook 插個egpu 落去打機用? 我咁既要求係唔係應該無乜需要?<br />\n<br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930fcace4f780121efa3e50e7db6f3457cda6ed3","tid":658431,"uid":41605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"blade stealth, 外型靚仔d"},{"pid":"f5721f63255a4cc6b16a46074c17092d6c27aae4","tid":658431,"uid":148636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"930fcace4f780121efa3e50e7db6f3457cda6ed3","tid":658431,"uid":41605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"blade stealth, 外型靚仔d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:08:14.000Z","msg":"外型兩部我都ok呀<br />\n我見兩部機睇落個spec差唔多, 功效上應該出到都差唔多?"},{"pid":"efe382eeaec78a8bde181f38ca7da3e3cd701bee","tid":658431,"uid":41605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5721f63255a4cc6b16a46074c17092d6c27aae4","tid":658431,"uid":148636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"930fcace4f780121efa3e50e7db6f3457cda6ed3","tid":658431,"uid":41605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T03:48:29.000Z","msg":"blade stealth, 外型靚仔d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:08:14.000Z","msg":"外型兩部我都ok呀<br />\n我見兩部機睇落個spec差唔多, 功效上應該出到都差唔多?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:11:04.000Z","msg":"理論上係"},{"pid":"9ff4a94d36eb409f776d4b2